# Slice 6: filesystem storage driver root (dev only).
# Mirrors the R2 layout schools/<schoolId>/imports/<jobId>/... — created
# lazily on first upload via apps/api's FilesystemStorageDriver. Prod
# uses STORAGE_DRIVER=r2 and this directory never appears.
.storage/

